title: Neff Outerwear
description:
http://www.neffheadwear.com/collections

Neff is proud to officially announce our entry into technical outerwear, complete with Neff Shred Fit technology. Shred Fit gives riders a comfortable full range of motion while also providing state of the art weather protection from the cold. Technical steez at its finest. Neff Outerwear features the perfect blend of form and fashion combining sick designs with Neff Shred Fit technology for optimal mobility on the mountain.Check Tim Humphreys out as he is thrown into the new Neff outwear collection. From the stylish Shred Fit jacket to the unique Character gloves, Neff Outerwear is a must have on the slopes.
